<div class="wims_thm"><h4>ThťorŤme</h4>
L'espace est muni d'un repŤre <strong>orthonormť</strong>
<span class="nowrap">\(\left(\mathrm{O}\,;\overrightarrow{i},\overrightarrow{j},\overrightarrow{k}\right)\).</span><br>
Soit \(\mathrm{A}\) et \(\mathrm{B}\) deux points de coordonnťes respectives
\((x_\mathrm{A}; y_\mathrm{A}; z_\mathrm{A})\) et
<span class="nowrap">\((x_\mathrm{B}; y_\mathrm{B}; z_\mathrm{B})\),</span> <strong>la distance</strong>
\(\mathrm{AB}\) des deux points \(\mathrm{A}\) et \(\mathrm{B}\) est donnťe
par&nbsp;:
<div class="wimscenter">
\(\sqrt{(x_\mathrm{B} - x_\mathrm{A})^2 + (y_\mathrm{B} - y_\mathrm{A})^2 +
(z_\mathrm{B} - z_\mathrm{A})^2}\)
</div>
</div>
